PN,40201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,FA former coastguard officer has
OL,8,Fcondemned the Maritime and Coastguard
OL,9,FAgency's decision to no longer pay
OL,10,Fvolunteers for callouts.
OL,12,FThere are around 400 volunteers, or
OL,13,F"coastguard rescue officers", in Devon
OL,14,Fand Cornwall.
OL,16,FUntil now, they've been compensated at
OL,17,F#11 an hour while attending incidents
OL,18,Fand training - but the MCA says it
OL,19,Fplans to axe those payments.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,FIt follows a Court of Appeal ruling
OL,8,Fthat coastguard rescue officers count
OL,9,Fas "workers" while they're carrying
OL,10,Fout a remunerated activity.
OL,12,FThe MCA has now decided to change how
OL,13,Fmuch compensation they're entitled to.
OL,14,FIt says a revised volunteer model will
OL,15,Fbest protect the future of the service.
OL,17,FFormer coastguard volunteer Damien
OL,18,FLambkin served for 18 years out of
OL,19,FFalmouth. He said the decision was
OL,20,F"pretty ridiculous".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F"It's not even minimum wage, but all
OL,8,Fthese brave men and women up and down
OL,9,Fthe country don't do it for the money.
OL,11,F"A callout isn't a quick job. It's
OL,12,Fupwards of three to six hours. You
OL,13,Fcould be out for an entire day. To
OL,14,Fknow that you were getting basic costs
OL,15,Fcovered meant the world.
OL,17,F"I can see experienced team members
OL,18,Fsaying, 'If I'm not going to get
OL,19,Fcompensated for this, why should I do
OL,20,Fit?'," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,FMr Lambkin added that most working
OL,8,Fpeople already couldn't volunteer
OL,9,Fbecause they'd have to leave work at
OL,10,Fshort notice to attend callouts.
OL,12,F"A lot of the team members are self-
OL,13,Femployed, because it's generally only
OL,14,Fthey who have the flexibility to down
OL,15,Ftools and go to an emergency.
OL,17,F"I've never quite understood how
OL,18,Femployees and employers allow their
OL,19,Fstaff to go. When they do get a call-
OL,20,Fout, their wages stop from their main
OL,21,Fjob," he explained.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,FHe added that the volunteers were
OL,8,F"putting their lives at risk" for the
OL,9,Fsake of others and at times enduring
OL,10,Fharrowing situations to help them.
OL,12,F"I was diagnosed with PTSD at the age
OL,13,Fof 26 directly as a result of events
OL,14,Fthat happened while in service of the
OL,15,Fcoastguard," Mr Lambkin said.
OL,17,FBefore teams are expected to attend
OL,18,Fcallouts, they need a huge amount of
OL,19,Ftraining.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F"You don't just turn up, get given a
OL,8,Fset of overalls, jump in a vehicle and
OL,9,Fthen throw yourself off a cliff to try
OL,10,Fto help people.
OL,12,F"There are hundreds of hours of
OL,13,Ftraining that go into being a rope
OL,14,Ftechnician, as mud rescues are one of
OL,15,Fthe most dangerous things you can do -
OL,16,Fas are cliff rescues.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F"Then most of the teams are also air-
OL,8,Fdeployable. Again, you don't just jump
OL,9,Fon a helicopter, you have to go
OL,10,Fthrough a lot of training to be able
OL,11,Fto do that.
OL,13,F"It's time-consuming. It eats up your
OL,14,Fweekends, time after work, time with
OL,15,Fyour family. There's between two and
OL,16,Ffour weeks of intense training to
OL,17,Fbecome a coastguard officer."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,FMr Lambkin also said that, although
OL,8,Fthe CROs were technically volunteers,
OL,9,Fthe Maritime and Coastguard Agency was
OL,10,Fa government organisation, not a
OL,11,Fcharity.
OL,13,FHe said: "As an employer, if I was to
OL,14,Fturn round and say to my staff,
OL,15,F'You're now all volunteers', I would
OL,16,Fbe opened up to a very substantial
OL,17,Flawsuit.
OL,19,F"The RNLI, for example, even they pay
OL,20,Ftheir crews when they're afloat and
OL,21,Fout doing work.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F"Men and women are putting their lives
OL,8,Fat risk. Do we think they should be
OL,9,Fcompensated for taking that risk? I
OL,10,Fthink the answer is a very clear 'yes,
OL,11,Fwe should'.
OL,13,F"If you want the best people to do
OL,14,Fthese search and rescue roles, you
OL,15,Fneed to start working with their
OL,16,Femployers as well so they can best
OL,17,Fsupport the individuals.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F"I think with certain organisations
OL,8,Fonce they get to a certain size they
OL,9,Fthink they can get away with anything.
OL,10,FIt takes a few brave people to stand
OL,11,Fup and say, 'You can't get away with
OL,12,Fthat'."
OL,14,FCoastguard 'vital' in emergency
OL,15,Fresponse to Boscastle floods
OL,17,FCarole Talboys, who was rescued from
OL,18,Fthe 2004 floods in Boscastle, said she
OL,19,Fowed the coastguard volunteers her
OL,20,Flife.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F"Getting that response in as quickly
OL,8,Fas possible, having the coastguard
OL,9,Fright on the spot when the water was
OL,10,Factually coming up, that was vital in
OL,11,Fgetting everybody else involved.
OL,13,F"They are on a direct line to the
OL,14,Fother emergency services - much more
OL,15,Fthan if an ordinary person had just
OL,16,Fcalled up. That was instantly picked
OL,17,Fup and treated very seriously.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,FRay, owner of the Toby Jug Cafe in the
OL,8,Fvillage, said: "We all see the good
OL,9,Fnews stories when they've rescued a
OL,10,Fdog but what you don't see are the
OL,11,Fstories that don't end well. Their
OL,12,Fpager goes off, they still go out,
OL,14,F"I think someone quoted it as being
OL,15,Fsomeone's darkest hour. They'll be
OL,16,Fthere for them. They're the fourth
OL,17,Femergency service. They are the people
OL,18,Fthat recover bodies and return them to
OL,19,Fthe families so they can grieve
OL,20,Fproperly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F'We need to change how the service
OL,8,Foperates'
OL,10,FA Maritime and Coastguard Agency
OL,11,Fspokesperson said: "After careful
OL,12,Fconsideration, we are moving the
OL,13,FCoastguard Rescue Service to a revised
OL,14,Fvolunteer model, to best protect the
OL,15,Ffuture of the service.
OL,26,@sD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F"This decision follows a legal
OL,8,Fjudgment, which means we need to
OL,9,Fchange how the service operates. This
OL,10,Fnew model protects choice, flexibility
OL,11,Fand the ability for people to
OL,12,Fvolunteer alongside their primary
OL,13,Femployment.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1781632101
OL,3,CFormer coastguard officer slams
OL,4,C'ridiculous' move to no longer pay
OL,5,Cvolunteers
OL,7,F"We deeply value and recognise the
OL,8,Fsignificant service Coastguard Rescue
OL,9,FOfficers provide along our coastline,
OL,10,Fand we will be supporting them during
OL,11,Fthis transition. The Coastguard Rescue
OL,12,FService will continue to maintain a
OL,13,Frobust, effective search and rescue
OL,14,Fresponse, ensuring the highest quality
OL,15,Fof service and levels of safety."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
